History



This is City of London Group plc


City of London Group plc (COLG) is a closed-ended investment company, investing in financial services businesses which provide finance to the SME and professional services sectors. It does this by financing trade and securing specialist funding throughout the supply chain to help fuel growth in these sectors, as major national and foreign banks limit new lending to those borrowers. COLG seeks to identify and exploit product niches and business models in these sectors where they are supported by strong day to day management teams, providing initial equity, working capital and seed funding for those teams.

COLG has developed specialist financing platforms, pledging significant seed funds to Credit Asset Management Limited, a provider of asset backed finance for the SME sector and commercial loans predominantly to professional practice firms, and Trade Finance Partners Limited, a trade finance provider to the SME market.



