					Full Description



		City of London Investment Group PLC is a United Kingdom-based institutional asset manager focused on closed-end fund investments. The Company offers developed, frontier, tactical asset allocation and private equity closed-end fund strategies. The Company's clients include the United States based pension funds, foundations and endowments. The Company operates through offices in London, the United States, Singapore and Dubai. It has over 150 institutional clients. It operates in the United States, Canada and Europe. The Company's principal operating subsidiary is City of London Investment Management Company Limited, which acts as its investment advisor and advises on approximately 50 accounts.
